releaseNotes:
We've taken on your feedback and made some changes to this version.

- Guest users now have the option to opt-in to push notifications so you don't miss out on any of the latest news or offers!
- We've added extra visibility for any promotions that are live so you can bag your favourite products
- We've also fixed some minor but very important bugs in order to give you the best Black Friday experience
description:
With all the ‘fits on the go, exclusive new activewear drops, notifications for what’s new and more, the Gymshark App gives you the best of Gymshark any time, anywhere. Because wherever you go, we move with you. Download the Gymshark App today and access:

THE LATEST PRODUCTS
Get the latest Gymshark ‘fits, first.

APP-ONLY ACCESS
Shop one-off, exclusive products only on the app and get early access to new product drops and sales.

CHECK THIS OUT
Get your favourite ‘fits faster by checking out swiftly and securely with multiple payment options to suit you.

SAVE WHAT YOU SEE
Save your most-loved activewear pieces to build your perfect outfit.

NEW & NOTIFIED
The only place you can get notifications for new drops.

FEATURED FAVOURITES
Shop featured looks you love.

FAMILY PERKS
Get an early look at the latest product launches and upcoming sales.

IN THE AREA? BOOK A CLASS AT OUR LONDON REGENT STREET STORE
Offering over 30 bookable classes every week, Gymshark Regent St will host a huge range of exercise classes including functional fitness, yoga, strength and HIIT. Plus 1:1 personal shopping experiences. There really will be something for everyone, and every class will be pre-bookable on our app. Spaces will be limited and it’s first come, first served, so book your slot to avoid missing out! 

Whatever your conditioning style, the Gymshark App is here to bring you the best of Gymshark activewear any time, anywhere. Clothes shopping with Gymshark is seamless, so you can get straight into your workout.

The Gymshark App is here to enrich your conditioning journey in many ways. So let’s start here; we’re getting exclusive. It’s the only place you can get notifications for new gym clothes drops to discover the latest launches first. Then get your favourite ‘fits faster by checking out swiftly and securely with flexible payment options to suit you plus next day delivery. Sound good?

There’s more than just clothes shopping. Save your most-loved pieces so you can easily view and build your next outfit, or shop featured activewear looks if you’re feeling inspired. Whatever your conditioning style, get the Gymshark you love, on the go.

As one of the family, you’ll get an early look at the latest ranges and product launches plus not only that, our app exclusives mean that you can shop one-off products too, not available anywhere else. 

The best of Gymshark any time, anywhere. Download today.
